    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not the same. everyone tells me it gets better, but how? how can it get better when the only person who actually saw me is gone? i feel like i'm just a shell. i move, i eat, i sleep... but i'm not really here. i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever does. it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life.",
